Interface SubScan

    All Known Subinterfaces:

    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface SubScan
extends Scan
    A SubScan operator represents the data scanned by a particular major/minor fragment. This is in contrast to a GroupScan operator, which represents all data scanned by a physical plan.
